                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Merry</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">San Salvador</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-07-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 13, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Merry reports Guatemala invading and fighting Honduras and Salvador.
                    Guatemala apparently retarding and Salvador anxious for peace. Asks to have <hi
                        rend="italic">Marblehead</hi> sent to Acajutla; says no other naval vessel
                    necessaiy at present.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
